<inglise> Whereas Council Directive 72/280/EEC of 31 July 1972 on the statistical surveys to be made by the Member States on milk and milk products (3) has been amended on several occasions; whereas, in the light of new amendments, it is in the interest of transparency to reformulate the provisions of the said Directive; </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: n&otilde;ukogu 31. juuli 1972. aasta direktiivi 72/280/EM&Uuml; liikmesriikide piima ja piimatoodete statistiliste vaatluste kohta on mitu korda muudetud; edasiste vajalike muudatuste t&otilde;ttu tuleks selguse saavutamiseks nimetatud direktiivi s&auml;tted &uuml;mber s&otilde;nastada; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas in order to carry out its duties under the Treaty and under Community provisions on the common organization of the market in milk and milk products the Commission needs reliable information about the production and use of milk and regular, reliable, short-term information about the delivery of milk to enterprises which treat or process milk and about the production of milk products in the Member States; </inglise>
<eesti> t&auml;itmaks asutamislepingust ning piima- ja piimatooteturu &uuml;hist korraldust k&auml;sitlevatest &uuml;henduse normidest tulenevaid kohustusi, vajab komisjon usaldusv&auml;&auml;rseid andmeid piima tootmise ning kasutamise kohta, samuti korrap&auml;rast, usaldusv&auml;&auml;rset ja l&uuml;hikest ajavahemikku k&auml;sitlevat teavet piimatarnete kohta piimat&ouml;&ouml;tlemisettev&otilde;tetele ning piimatoodete valmistamise kohta liikmesriikides; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas surveys on the production and use of milk on the farm should be conducted in accordance with uniform criteria and in greater detail, and monthly surveys should be made in all Member States in enterprises which process milk; </inglise>
<eesti> p&otilde;llumajandusettev&otilde;ttes piimatootmist ja -kasutamist h&otilde;lmavad vaatlused tuleks teha &uuml;htsete kriteeriumide alusel ning &uuml;ksikasjalikumalt, samuti tuleks liikmesriikide k&otilde;ikides piimat&ouml;&ouml;tlemisettev&otilde;tetes teha igakuiseid vaatlusi; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, in order to obtain comparable results, common criteria should be fixed as regards the scope of the survey, the characteristics to be noted and the survey procedure; </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;rreldavate tulemuste saamiseks tuleks kehtestada vaatluse ulatuse, arvessev&otilde;etavate omaduste ja vaatlusmenetluse &uuml;hised kriteeriumid; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas experience acquired in implementing the previous rules has shown that it would be useful to simplify the provisions, in particular by abolishing the requirement to provide weekly results; </inglise>
<eesti> varasemate eeskirjade rakendamisel omandatud kogemused on n&auml;idanud, et kasulik oleks nende s&auml;tteid lihtsustada, loobudes eelk&otilde;ige n&auml;dalaaruannete esitamise n&otilde;udest; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, in view of the growing importance of the milk-protein content of milk products the appropriate steps must be taken; </inglise>
